{"tid":326132,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[行程求批] 7月尾雲南之旅 (另搵人一齊入雨崩","createTime":"2017-07-17T17:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T15:14:36.000Z","uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fdf78c9aa525f75c3f26c8bd39c1b2de225aa224","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:53:07.000Z","msg":"行程:<br />\n7/22: 香港 - 昆明<br />\n7/23: 昆明 - 麗江<br />\n7/24: 麗江 (白沙古鎮 束河古城<br />\n7/25: 麗江 (搵下價錢 平就去拉市海遊船 茶馬古道騎馬 <br />\n7/26: 麗江 - 瀘沽湖<br />\n7/27: 瀘沽湖 (電單車環湖)<br />\n7/28: 瀘沽湖 - 麗江 - 香格里拉 (搵人併車!!!)<br />\n7/29: 香格里拉 - 飛來寺 (搵人併車!!!)<br />\n7/30: 飛來寺 - 西當 - 雨崩<br />\n7/31: 雨崩 <br />\n8/1: 雨崩 <br />\n8/2: 雨崩 - 尼農 - 香格里拉<br />\n8/3: 香格里拉 (獨克宗古城<br />\n8/4: 香格里拉 - 麗江 - 大理<br />\n8/5: 大理 (大理古城<br />\n8/6: 大理 (雙廊or沙溪<br />\n8/7: 大理- 昆明 - 香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人7月尾/8月頭會係雲南想入雨崩<br />\n時間可以大家再就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有意留 Telegram id<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6851ec2c0c321e6a33309bdb1f146a76f5e623e","tid":326132,"uid":26791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:55:07.000Z","msg":"之前併車入左飛來寺 後黎聽人講有大包入去 平好多 你可以搵下"},{"pid":"a3999ccf209ef4234feb939936be90f027a03dda","tid":326132,"uid":26791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:55:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前併車入左飛來寺 後黎聽人講有大<span style=\"color: red;\">巴</span>入去 平好多 你可以搵下</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14d9a219e6cb271393597df0a1f0600df9657df","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:59:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前併車入左飛來寺 後黎聽人講有大<span style=\"color: red;\">巴</span>入去 平好多 你可以搵下</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要係想併車入西當(呢段路一定要併車入)同搵人同行 有咩事上黎都有個照應"},{"pid":"d1ea81d64afc6f4ef3971e3ad48c83ddc592237f","tid":326132,"uid":84122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T19:03:15.000Z","msg":"我去瀘沽湖果陣 好多同行既人都係去完拉市海再到瀘沽湖<br />\n佢地既意見係 如果會去瀘沽湖就唔洗去拉市海<br />\n利申 岩岩6月去完雲南 不過無去到拉市海"},{"pid":"28dfe5a9cfb6920d11dbba7005bff65bf0ac70b8","tid":326132,"uid":61643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T19:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前併車入左飛來寺 後黎聽人講有大<span style=\"color: red;\">巴</span>入去 平好多 你可以搵下</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要係想併車入西當(呢段路一定要併車入)同搵人同行 有咩事上黎都有個照應</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香格里拉有班車直達飛來寺，第二日可併車到西當（唔洗怕拼唔到，司機多到爆）<br />\n<br />\n西當入雨崩一條大路而且人多，危險性極極極極低<br />\n<br />\n經尼農出雨崩，會有車在出口等客，會經德欽番飛來寺，如果行李跟身，可直接在德欽坐車回麗江<br />\n<br />\n若入雨崩前行李寄放在飛來寺，要先回去拎，若行程唔急可休息一日<br />\n<br />\n雨崩有三景點：冰湖、神湖、神瀑，個人建議去晒。冰湖、神湖各需一個全日，體力好可最後一日去完神瀑直接經尼農出<br />\n<br />\n六月先去完雨崩，超正"},{"pid":"a6e7aeb633eea0d8b9fb5509c7425a84c3deb232","tid":326132,"uid":61643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T19:54:42.000Z","msg":"若想節省時間，可第一日晚坐火車到麗江，第二朝早就到"},{"pid":"7442f6f39ac7db13340cc9b6f933690fb5ab46e3","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前併車入左飛來寺 後黎聽人講有大<span style=\"color: red;\">巴</span>入去 平好多 你可以搵下</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要係想併車入西當(呢段路一定要併車入)同搵人同行 有咩事上黎都有個照應</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香格里拉有班車直達飛來寺，第二日可併車到西當（唔洗怕拼唔到，司機多到爆）<br />\n<br />\n西當入雨崩一條大路而且人多，危險性極極極極低<br />\n<br />\n經尼農出雨崩，會有車在出口等客，會經德欽番飛來寺，如果行李跟身，可直接在德欽坐車回麗江<br />\n<br />\n若入雨崩前行李寄放在飛來寺，要先回去拎，若行程唔急可休息一日<br />\n<br />\n雨崩有三景點：冰湖、神湖、神瀑，個人建議去晒。冰湖、神湖各需一個全日，體力好可最後一日去完神瀑直接經尼農出<br />\n<br />\n六月先去完雨崩，超正</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks bro"},{"pid":"f16483d3d24ec174c26db112914e6240976c63e7","tid":326132,"uid":22496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打我雨崩果段時間同你一樣 可以一齊tg 我"},{"pid":"b43960d24ed5ef85b037d4ef90baabcae671d38a","tid":326132,"uid":20074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:18:09.000Z","msg":"麗江玩唔到咁多日，瀘沽湖之前唔比租電動車，香格里拉玩唔到咁多日，要去松贊x寺<br />\n雨崩可以玩多日"},{"pid":"95b9887f1127ff25c86344fc23eb5b19d9b9a9fa","tid":326132,"uid":20074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:22:05.000Z","msg":"其實好多地方都唔洗玩咁耐<br />\n大理麗江香格里拉飛來寺瀘沽湖最多都係2日玩完"},{"pid":"4e65e546759b05aa5d5f7728f3f5b95534afc2d5","tid":326132,"uid":91562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:23:53.000Z","msg":"第一日直接搭多一程飛麗江啦，留係昆明無乜意思"},{"pid":"e25a59f6191b1360fc2a0d6811706d5fc640e5ad","tid":326132,"uid":91562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前併車入左飛來寺 後黎聽人講有大<span style=\"color: red;\">巴</span>入去 平好多 你可以搵下</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要係想併車入西當(呢段路一定要併車入)同搵人同行 有咩事上黎都有個照應</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香格里拉有班車直達飛來寺，第二日可併車到西當（唔洗怕拼唔到，司機多到爆）<br />\n<br />\n西當入雨崩一條大路而且人多，危險性極極極極低<br />\n<br />\n經尼農出雨崩，會有車在出口等客，會經德欽番飛來寺，如果行李跟身，可直接在德欽坐車回麗江<br />\n<br />\n若入雨崩前行李寄放在飛來寺，要先回去拎，若行程唔急可休息一日<br />\n<br />\n雨崩有三景點：冰湖、神湖、神瀑，個人建議去晒。冰湖、神湖各需一個全日，體力好可最後一日去完神瀑直接經尼農出<br />\n<br />\n六月先去完雨崩，超正</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thanks bro</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去果陣d人話神湖條路仲係封哂雪去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都好，有個原因可以再去多次"},{"pid":"c69cdfc9b56186c888412f8696a38da19d900443","tid":326132,"uid":72481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:31:57.000Z","msg":"去青旅住識人入雨崩啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vk5089c3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvk5089c3&h=aee854a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33c2e0ad5372855ebe024d752a596eaeea4b3dad","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T13:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一日直接搭多一程飛麗江啦，留係昆明無乜意思</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買唔到火車飛 得無坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6af7bdcf1bc0ebe6413cd9a264f2b549ec26606","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d794da96b629f61d740c9aaf5cc37bc50602e0","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:44:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去青旅住識人入雨崩啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vk5089c3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvk5089c3&h=aee854a3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n堅正 巴打係幾時影架"},{"pid":"67d2a46a94ea9dd6888d5d852543fe957a2b4447","tid":326132,"uid":19475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:54:49.000Z","msg":"巴打 我想問你昆明去麗江你會飛機定係火車?"},{"pid":"d857cfd9f0db79b4d89db76b32c020d3411b0179","tid":326132,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T23:20:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麗江玩唔到咁多日，瀘沽湖之前唔比租電動車，香格里拉玩唔到咁多日，要去松贊x寺<br />\n雨崩可以玩多日</blockquote><br />\n2日都玩唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑死人咩，定係去打卡就去過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n瀘沽湖唔好電單車，好撚危險，包車環湖就得，人少拼車<br />\n另外香格里拉巴士站有車直到大理，同司機講古城口落就得,時間5小時，唔駛再番麗江<br />\n<br />\n最後7-8 雨季又熱又撚多人，祝好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662c212a98b63ac87c167e55598990f6fc30a413","tid":326132,"uid":72481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>麗江玩唔到咁多日，瀘沽湖之前唔比租電動車，香格里拉玩唔到咁多日，要去松贊x寺<br />\n雨崩可以玩多日</blockquote><br />\n2日都玩唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑死人咩，定係去打卡就去過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n瀘沽湖唔好電單車，好撚危險，包車環湖就得，人少拼車<br />\n另外香格里拉巴士站有車直到大理，同司機講古城口落就得,時間5小時，唔駛再番麗江<br />\n<br />\n最後7-8 雨季又熱又撚多人，祝好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n7 8月點會熱，高山位置日日都好涼就真"},{"pid":"102a5cf7301e931de0408eab9573e0745cc11d15","tid":326132,"uid":72481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:02:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去青旅住識人入雨崩啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vk5089c3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvk5089c3&h=aee854a3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n堅正 巴打係幾時影架</blockquote><br />\n計計下都5年前了"},{"pid":"aee828d11f2686f07fd2c8135e01afb51076a57b","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:42:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>麗江玩唔到咁多日，瀘沽湖之前唔比租電動車，香格里拉玩唔到咁多日，要去松贊x寺<br />\n雨崩可以玩多日</blockquote><br />\n2日都玩唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑死人咩，定係去打卡就去過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n瀘沽湖唔好電單車，好撚危險，包車環湖就得，人少拼車<br />\n另外香格里拉巴士站有車直到大理，同司機講古城口落就得,時間5小時，唔駛再番麗江<br />\n<br />\n最後7-8 雨季又熱又撚多人，祝好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n7 8月點會熱，高山位置日日都好涼就真</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n定係去打卡就去過&lt;&lt;&lt; 呢句係咪佢自己同佢自己講<br />\n我都心諗成3,4千海拔邊會熱<br />\n之前我都7,8月去西藏 凍到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d27415ec1cbe38c707fba402e7b4fbb90e317e5","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1086d10dfce427a15ac12b36591e1d232f91a842","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b973a26f04589aaffb51d51b3d3b493e593e1ffe","tid":326132,"uid":100915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:49:15.000Z","msg":"下雨崩可以住雪龍客棧 老闆娘超好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c72960cbf98971ee781789b8155b08a3ed06e2","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下雨崩可以住雪龍客棧 老闆娘超好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4210bff2680feb74f01441e148d7c13a2fc6a5","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T13:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c4ef1670a9b2c22855345933fb6af14712d8eb","tid":326132,"uid":47584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T13:56:05.000Z","msg":"香格里拉去飛來寺可以唔洗拼車<br />\n有大巴由香格里拉去德欽<br />\n<br />\n去到德欽再搭10蚊的士就入到去飛來寺"},{"pid":"5ac7172d3f9ed6abf534aeb94e90cbdec039c470","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T15:20:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香格里拉去飛來寺可以唔洗拼車<br />\n有大巴由香格里拉去德欽<br />\n<br />\n去到德欽再搭10蚊的士就入到去飛來寺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要係想搵人一直拼到去西當<br />\n想係香格里拉開始搵人入西當<br />\n入西當好似一定要拼車?"},{"pid":"e2b292b73573b9ad4ca8bace0ed84ad2e7345767","tid":326132,"uid":16990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T15:24:50.000Z","msg":"7/27: 瀘沽湖 (電單車環湖)<br />\n<br />\n岩岩係雲南返黎想提下你<br />\n<br />\n呢度禁止晒電單車，你出多多錢都唔會租到"},{"pid":"e6d827b205b01bc1e70b9f29d7651c19762c12e5","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T15:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7/27: 瀘沽湖 (電單車環湖)<br />\n<br />\n岩岩係雲南返黎想提下你<br />\n<br />\n呢度禁止晒電單車，你出多多錢都唔會租到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n電動車有冇禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果都禁埋咁唯有用單車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打你去左邊玩左咩 分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc11c1bfdd62679dd70bf0d48f1d16ea7ecca7e","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T19:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ecd997c3612b02d08baea018482917e1c6bc5b5","tid":326132,"uid":115065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"我今日出發昆明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行程同你都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未plan 幾時但會去雨崩 可以拼車啊一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但冇tg 喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72842074f5b60e19d4979157828edb8d4851454","tid":326132,"uid":115065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T02:39:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我今日出發昆明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行程同你都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未plan 幾時但會去雨崩 可以拼車啊一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但冇tg 喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行程係咪照抄同一個blog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一撚樣"},{"pid":"44687d8fcdcb2fa75e8f4f972542f48273eda12b","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T03:34:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我今日出發昆明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行程同你都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未plan 幾時但會去雨崩 可以拼車啊一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但冇tg 喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行程係咪照抄同一個blog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一撚樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以話係 可以話唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為 距離問題 有部份行程一定要咁PLAN<br />\n唔係仲要走回頭路 同埋哂時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e244f90b755751b3293f935be4049d3f502ca5","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T03:34:45.000Z","msg":"我知你講邊個BLOG 我睇左好多遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee7ed25c3e97ef45e045c17fee64f54fc7ed412","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T03:35:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我今日出發昆明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行程同你都差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未plan 幾時但會去雨崩 可以拼車啊一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但冇tg 喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁巴打你有冇WECHAT OR你比你電話我<br />\n番大陸沒WECHAT真係唔店 雖然唔想裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388ee1b84da3ee2e4e477a68447a5e6e47c3aee9","tid":326132,"uid":47584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T03:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香格里拉去飛來寺可以唔洗拼車<br />\n有大巴由香格里拉去德欽<br />\n<br />\n去到德欽再搭10蚊的士就入到去飛來寺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要係想搵人一直拼到去西當<br />\n想係香格里拉開始搵人入西當<br />\n入西當好似一定要拼車?</blockquote><br />\n唔洗咁快揾定<br />\n去到飛來寺再揾人拼都得<br />\n依家旺季大把人入去<br />\n<br />\n事關我上年一月初超淡季都喺飛來寺揾到人併車入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ce82dd160daa4a4dbb905074175e8b13276c63","tid":326132,"uid":47584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香格里拉去飛來寺可以唔洗拼車<br />\n有大巴由香格里拉去德欽<br />\n<br />\n去到德欽再搭10蚊的士就入到去飛來寺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要係想搵人一直拼到去西當<br />\n想係香格里拉開始搵人入西當<br />\n入西當好似一定要拼車?</blockquote><br />\n唔洗咁快揾定<br />\n去到飛來寺再揾人拼都得<br />\n依家旺季大把人入去<br />\n<br />\n事關我上年一月初超淡季都喺飛來寺揾到人併車入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋香格里拉去飛來寺都要好撚耐<br />\n通常啲人由香格里拉坐完大巴入德欽，再入飛來寺<br />\n都會喺飛來寺stay一晚先<br />\n<br />\n第二朝起身睇完日照金山再出發<br />\n順便可以擺低啲大件行李<br />\n唔洗揹住一大袋野入雨崩 (海拔三四千行路都幾係野)<br />\n<br />\n而且西當行入雨崩段路<br />\n快則5，6個鐘<br />\n慢則7，8個鐘<br />\n甚至更耐啲都有<br />\n<br />\n如果你一日由香格里拉直爆入去雨崩<br />\n我驚你夜晚先入到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35fdf28fa6aab2ff216829326f9c46f81b14bc5a","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香格里拉去飛來寺可以唔洗拼車<br />\n有大巴由香格里拉去德欽<br />\n<br />\n去到德欽再搭10蚊的士就入到去飛來寺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要係想搵人一直拼到去西當<br />\n想係香格里拉開始搵人入西當<br />\n入西當好似一定要拼車?</blockquote><br />\n唔洗咁快揾定<br />\n去到飛來寺再揾人拼都得<br />\n依家旺季大把人入去<br />\n<br />\n事關我上年一月初超淡季都喺飛來寺揾到人併車入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋香格里拉去飛來寺都要好撚耐<br />\n通常啲人由香格里拉坐完大巴入德欽，再入飛來寺<br />\n都會喺飛來寺stay一晚先<br />\n<br />\n第二朝起身睇完日照金山再出發<br />\n順便可以擺低啲大件行李<br />\n唔洗揹住一大袋野入雨崩 (海拔三四千行路都幾係野)<br />\n<br />\n而且西當行入雨崩段路<br />\n快則5，6個鐘<br />\n慢則7，8個鐘<br />\n甚至更耐啲都有<br />\n<br />\n如果你一日由香格里拉直爆入去雨崩<br />\n我驚你夜晚先入到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我打錯 我沒打算入飛來寺 只係打算到德欽<br />\n應該係睇BLOG多 當左德欽同飛來寺係同一個地方<br />\n呢個錯誤我都係開左POST之後再搵資料既時候發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我會用一日由香格里拉到德欽 之後往一夜<br />\n第2日睇日出 之後就出發入西當"},{"pid":"b7640fd1ec209f81d63ed4f104549ca6635fc1d3","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"搵唔到都打算單拖入<br />\n我有朋友上年呢個時候到去過<br />\n話好多人入 幾安全"},{"pid":"eb13b55443e0f8b2ac6739c4563b2ff3e160980a","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T08:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41fefed64f855c499e3efcf8906091ddc5c5f1cc","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ef459d2e26d656487f2b0895ec8393922a5f78","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4dee7ae0134c0a5d5dfa5da41f69d8bf51f411f","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109b6db457b1d2e4452ed316140e09c142f5eac2","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbdabe9b0492f0fe562e508ac5c5e0d7348a786","tid":326132,"uid":61643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:29:53.000Z","msg":"五月尾單拖去完<br />\n無咩難度同危險<br />\n但上神湖的話最好結伴<br />\n落雨都要小心，落山「煽」到顛"},{"pid":"3254f9dd3d090d7b6e5c03554eefdc8758f39987","tid":326132,"uid":117285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香格里拉去飛來寺可以唔洗拼車<br />\n有大巴由香格里拉去德欽<br />\n<br />\n去到德欽再搭10蚊的士就入到去飛來寺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要係想搵人一直拼到去西當<br />\n想係香格里拉開始搵人入西當<br />\n入西當好似一定要拼車?</blockquote><br />\n唔洗咁快揾定<br />\n去到飛來寺再揾人拼都得<br />\n依家旺季大把人入去<br />\n<br />\n事關我上年一月初超淡季都喺飛來寺揾到人併車入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋香格里拉去飛來寺都要好撚耐<br />\n通常啲人由香格里拉坐完大巴入德欽，再入飛來寺<br />\n都會喺飛來寺stay一晚先<br />\n<br />\n第二朝起身睇完日照金山再出發<br />\n順便可以擺低啲大件行李<br />\n唔洗揹住一大袋野入雨崩 (海拔三四千行路都幾係野)<br />\n<br />\n而且西當行入雨崩段路<br />\n快則5，6個鐘<br />\n慢則7，8個鐘<br />\n甚至更耐啲都有<br />\n<br />\n如果你一日由香格里拉直爆入去雨崩<br />\n我驚你夜晚先入到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我打錯 我沒打算入飛來寺 只係打算到德欽<br />\n應該係睇BLOG多 當左德欽同飛來寺係同一個地方<br />\n呢個錯誤我都係開左POST之後再搵資料既時候發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我會用一日由香格里拉到德欽 之後往一夜<br />\n第2日睇日出 之後就出發入西當</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇日出緊係stay飛來寺啦<br />\n坐香格里拉去德欽大巴 只要你見佢係行山裝扮 基本上有99%都係入雨崩 根本唔使怕冇人同你併車<br />\n大巴去到德欽唔落車補多5蚊就係去飛來寺<br />\n一排雪山非常莊觀<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/232706_f73854cd7cde1801086f3811d0272a55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F232706_f73854cd7cde1801086f3811d0272a55.jpg&h=27076d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德欽感覺好污糟同城市化 應該唔會住得舒服"},{"pid":"e5052328a8871bbfc636f296a026bc9ea501b69b","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:47:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五月尾單拖去完<br />\n無咩難度同危險<br />\n但上神湖的話最好結伴<br />\n落雨都要小心，落山「煽」到顛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有對深狗牙既鞋 希望唔好咁煽"},{"pid":"f0b02f2551047610e3028a4a3c49127b7bf95669","tid":326132,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:48:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香格里拉去飛來寺可以唔洗拼車<br />\n有大巴由香格里拉去德欽<br />\n<br />\n去到德欽再搭10蚊的士就入到去飛來寺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n主要係想搵人一直拼到去西當<br />\n想係香格里拉開始搵人入西當<br />\n入西當好似一定要拼車?</blockquote><br />\n唔洗咁快揾定<br />\n去到飛來寺再揾人拼都得<br />\n依家旺季大把人入去<br />\n<br />\n事關我上年一月初超淡季都喺飛來寺揾到人併車入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋香格里拉去飛來寺都要好撚耐<br />\n通常啲人由香格里拉坐完大巴入德欽，再入飛來寺<br />\n都會喺飛來寺stay一晚先<br />\n<br />\n第二朝起身睇完日照金山再出發<br />\n順便可以擺低啲大件行李<br />\n唔洗揹住一大袋野入雨崩 (海拔三四千行路都幾係野)<br />\n<br />\n而且西當行入雨崩段路<br />\n快則5，6個鐘<br />\n慢則7，8個鐘<br />\n甚至更耐啲都有<br />\n<br />\n如果你一日由香格里拉直爆入去雨崩<br />\n我驚你夜晚先入到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我打錯 我沒打算入飛來寺 只係打算到德欽<br />\n應該係睇BLOG多 當左德欽同飛來寺係同一個地方<br />\n呢個錯誤我都係開左POST之後再搵資料既時候發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我會用一日由香格里拉到德欽 之後往一夜<br />\n第2日睇日出 之後就出發入西當</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇日出緊係stay飛來寺啦<br />\n坐香格里拉去德欽大巴 只要你見佢係行山裝扮 基本上有99%都係入雨崩 根本唔使怕冇人同你併車<br />\n大巴去到德欽唔落車補多5蚊就係去飛來寺<br />\n一排雪山非常莊觀<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/232706_f73854cd7cde1801086f3811d0272a55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F232706_f73854cd7cde1801086f3811d0272a55.jpg&h=27076d83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德欽感覺好污糟同城市化 應該唔會住得舒服</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過唔知有冇時間去睇<br />\n到左德欽睇下幾點先"}]}